lead_paragraph: Antoine Griezmann and Yannick Carrasco each conjured moments of magic as Atletico Madrid recaptured top spot in La Liga from Barcelona with a hard-fought 2-0 victory at Celta Vigo on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Atletico Surge Back Above Barca to the Top of La Liga
headline.main: Atletico Surge Back Above Barca to the Top of La Liga
